@startuml
title InsightsRadar v1 - End-to-End Smoke Validation Loop

actor Operator
participant "Cron / Manual Trigger" as Trigger
participant "Worker Ingest" as Ingest
participant "Cloudflare RSS" as RSS
queue "Queue" as Q
participant "Worker Digest Consumer" as Digest
database "D1" as D1
collections "R2" as R2
participant "Web App" as Web
participant "Worker API" as API

Operator -> Trigger: run smoke sequence
Trigger -> Ingest: start ingest
Ingest -> RSS: fetch feed
Ingest -> D1: upsert candidates
Ingest -> Q: enqueue jobs

Q -> Digest: deliver jobs
Digest -> D1: read + update terminal state
Digest -> R2: write artifacts

Operator -> Web: open /
Web -> API: GET /api/articles
API -> D1: query processed tiles
D1 --> API: feed rows
API --> Web: tile payload

Operator -> Web: open summary route
Web -> API: GET /api/articles/summary?id=...
API -> D1: summary payload lookup
API --> Web: summary data

Operator -> Web: open detail route
Web -> API: GET /api/articles/detail?id=...
API -> D1: detail payload lookup
API --> Web: detail data

Operator -> Operator: mark smoke pass/fail

@enduml
